  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK315">
<l>aṟiviṉā ṉākuva tuṇṭō piṟitunōy</l>
<l>taṉṉōypōṟ pōṟṟāk kaṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What benefit has he derived from his knowledge, who does not endeavour to keep off pain from another as much as from himself ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
